quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,(th) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  20,2,ma 'anzalna ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - alqran; ltshqa bima la taqat lak bih min aleml
  20,3,"lkn 'anzalnah mwezt; lytdhkr bih man yakhaf eiqab allh, fytqyh bi'ada' alfrayd wajtnab almharm"
  20,4,hdha alquran tanzil min allah aladhi khalaq al'ard walsmwat alela
  20,5,alrhmn ealaa alearsh astwa 'aya airtafae wela astwa' ylyq bjlalh wezmth
  20,6,"lh ma fi alsmwat wama fi al'ard wama baynahuma wama taht alard, khalqana wmulkana wtdbyrana"
  20,7,"w'in tajhar - 'ayuha alrasul - balqwl, ftelnh 'aw tkhfh, fa'iina allah la yakhfaa ealayh shy', yaelam alsira wama hu akhfa min alsiri mimaa thddith bih nfsk"
  20,8,"allh aldhy la mebwd bihaqi 'iilaa hw, lah wahdah al'asma' alkamilat fi alhsn"
  20,9,whl 'atak - 'ayuha alrasul - khabar musaa bin eimran ealayh alslam?
  20,10,"hyn ra'aa fi allayl narana mwqdt faqal lahlh: antaziruu laqad absrt narana, laealiy ajyykm minha bshelt tstdfywn bha, wtwqdwn biha narana akhra، 'aw 'ajid eindaha hadyana ydlna ealaa altryq"
  20,11,"flma 'ataa musaa tilk alnaar nadah allh: ya mwsa، 'iiniy 'ana rabuk fakhlae nelyk, 'iinak alan bwady \"twa\" aldhy barkth, wdhlk astedadana lmnajat rbh"
  20,12,"flma 'ataa musaa tilk alnaar nadah allh: ya mwsa، 'iiniy 'ana rabuk fakhlae nelyk, 'iinak alan bwady \"twa\" aldhy barkth, wdhlk astedadana lmnajat rbh"
  20,13,"w'iny akhtartuk ya musaa lrsalty, fastamie lima ywha 'iilayk mny"
  20,14,"'inny 'ana allah la mebwd bihaqi 'iilaa ana, la sharik ly, faebudni whdy, wa'aqim alsalat ltdhkrny fyha"
  20,15,"'in alssaeat alty yubeth fiha alnaas atyt la bd min wqweha, 'akad 'ukhfiha min nfsy, fkyf yaelamuha 'ahad min almkhlwqyn; likay tujza kulu nafs bima eamilat fi aldunya min khayr 'aw shr"
  20,16,"fala ysrfnnak - ya musaa - ean al'iiman biha walastedad laha man la yusadiq bwqweha wala yaemal lha, watabae hawaa nfsh, fkdhdhab bha, fthlk"
  20,17,wma hadhih alty fi yaminik ya mwsa?
  20,18,"qal mwsa: hi easay aetmd ealayha fi almshy, wahzz biha alshjr; ltrea ghanami ma ytsaqt min wrqh, wali fiha manafie akhra"
  20,19,"qal allah lmwsa: 'alq esak"
  20,20,"falqaha musaa ealaa alard, fanqlbt bi'iidhn allah hayatan tsea, fraa musaa amrana ezymana wwla harbana"
  20,21,"qal allah lmwsa: khudh alhyt, wala takhaf mnha, sawf neydha esana kama kanat fi haltha alawla. wadmum yadak 'iilaa jnbk taht aleadud takhruj bayda' kalthlj min ghyr brs; litakun lak elamt akhra"
  20,22,"qal allah lmwsa: khudh alhyt, wala takhaf mnha, sawf neydha esana kama kanat fi haltha alawla. wadmum yadak 'iilaa jnbk taht aleadud takhruj bayda' kalthlj min ghyr brs; litakun lak elamt akhra"
  20,23,"felna dhlk; likay nuriak - ya musaa - min adltna alkubraa ma ydll ealaa qdrtna, wezym sltanna, wsht rsaltk"
  20,24,"adhhb - ya musaa - 'iilaa frewn; 'iinah qad tajawuz qadaruh wtmrrad ealaa rbh, fadeh 'iilaa tawhid allah webadth"
  20,25,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,26,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,27,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,28,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,29,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,30,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,31,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,32,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,33,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,34,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,35,"qal mwsa: rabi wssie li sdry, wsahhil li amry, wa'atlaq lisani bfsyh almntq; lyfhmu klamy. wajeal liy mueayanaan min ahly, harun akhy. qawwiny bih wshdd bih zhry, wa'ashrikh maei fi alnubuat wtblygh alrsalt; kay nnzhk baltsbyh kthyrana, wanadhkurak kathirana fnhmdk. 'iinak kunt bina bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayk shay' min afealna"
  20,36,"qal allh: qad aetytk kl ma sa'alt ya mwsa"
  20,37,"wlqd 'aneamna ealayk - ya musaa - qabl hadhih alnaemat niemat akhra, hin kunt rdyeana, fanjynak min batsh frewn"
  20,38,"wdhlk hin alhmna ammak: 'ana dey abnak musaa baed wiladatih fi altabwt, thuma atrhyh fi alnyl, fasawf ylqyh alnayl ealaa alsahl, fyakhdhh fireawn eaduiy wedwh. wa'alqayt ealayk mahabatan miniy fsrt bdhlk mhbwbana bayn alebad, wlitrba ealaa eayni wafi hfzy. wafi alayat 'iithbat sifat aleayn lilah - subhanah wteala - kama ylyq bjlalh wkmalh"
  20,39,"wdhlk hin alhmna ammak: 'ana dey abnak musaa baed wiladatih fi altabwt, thuma atrhyh fi alnyl, fasawf ylqyh alnayl ealaa alsahl, fyakhdhh fireawn eaduiy wedwh. wa'alqayt ealayk mahabatan miniy fsrt bdhlk mhbwbana bayn alebad, wlitrba ealaa eayni wafi hfzy. wafi alayat 'iithbat sifat aleayn lilah - subhanah wteala - kama ylyq bjlalh wkmalh"
  20,40,"wmnnna ealayk hin tamshi 'ukhtuk ttbek thuma taqul liman akhdhwk: hal 'adulukum ealaa min ykfulh, wyrdeh lkm? frddnak 'iilaa ammik baed ma srt fi 'aydi frewn; kay ttyb nafsiha bslamtk min algharaq walqtl, wala tahzan ealaa faqdk, waqatalat alrajul alqbty khataan fanajaynak min ghamm fielk wkhwf alqtl, wabtlynak abtla', fkhrjt khayfana 'iilaa 'ahl \"mdyn\", fmktht sinin fyhm, thuma jit min \"mdyn\" fi almaweid aldhy qddarnah l'irsalk mjyyana mwafqana lqdr allah w'iradth, wal'amr kulah lilah tabarak wteala"
  20,41,"wanemt ealayk - ya musaa - hadhih alnaeam ajtba' miniy lk, wakhtyarana lrsalty, walblagh eny, walqiam bamry wnhyy"
  20,42,"adhhb - ya musaa - 'ant wa'akhuk harun biayati aldalt ealaa alwhyty wkmal qdrty wasadaq rsaltk, wala tadeufa ean mdawmt dhkry. adhhaba meana 'iilaa frewn; 'iinah qad jawz alhadi fi alkufr walzlm, faqula lah qawlana ltyfana; laealah yatadhakar 'aw yakhaf rbh"
  20,43,"adhhab - ya musaa - 'ant wa'akhuk harun biayati aldalt ealaa alwhyty wkmal qdrty wasadaq rsaltk, wala tadeufa ean mdawmt dhkry. adhhaba meana 'iilaa frewn; 'iinah qad jawz alhadi fi alkufr walzlm, faqula lah qawlana ltyfana; laealah yatadhakar 'aw yakhaf rbh"
  20,44,"adhhb - ya musaa - 'ant wa'akhuk harun biayati aldalt ealaa alwhyty wkmal qdrty wasadaq rsaltk, wala tadeufa ean mdawmt dhkry. adhhaba meana 'iilaa frewn; 'iinah qad jawz alhadi fi alkufr walzlm, faqula lah qawlana ltyfana; laealah yatadhakar 'aw yakhaf rbh"
  20,45,"qal musaa wharwn: rabana 'iinana nakhaf 'an yeajlna baleqwbt, 'aw 'an ytmrd ealaa alhaqi fala yqblh"
  20,46,"qal allah lmwsa wharwn: la takhafa min frewn; f'inny maeakuma 'asmae klamkma wara afealkma, fadhhaba 'iilayh wqwla lh: 'iinana rswlan 'iilayk min rabik 'ana 'atlaq bani 'israyyl, wala tkllifhm ma la ytyqwn min alaemal, qad atynak bdlalt mejzt min rabik tadulu ealaa sadaqana fi dewtna, walslamt min eadhab allah taealaa liman atabae hdah. 'iina rabak qad awha 'iilayna an eadhabah ealaa man kdhdhab wa'aerid ean dewth wshryeth"
  20,47,"qal allah lmwsa wharwn: la takhafa min frewn; f'inny maeakuma 'asmae klamkma wara afealkma, fadhhaba 'iilayh wqwla lh: 'iinana rswlan 'iilayk min rabik 'ana 'atlaq bani 'israyyl, wala tkllifhm ma la ytyqwn min alaemal, qad atynak bdlalt mejzt min rabik tadulu ealaa sadaqana fi dewtna, walslamt min eadhab allah taealaa liman atabae hdah. 'iina rabak qad awha 'iilayna an eadhabah ealaa man kdhdhab wa'aerid ean dewth wshryeth"
  20,48,"qal allah lmwsa wharwn: la takhafa min frewn; f'inny maeakuma 'asmae klamkma wara afealkma, fadhhaba 'iilayh wqwla lh: 'iinana rswlan 'iilayk min rabik 'ana 'atlaq bani 'israyyl, wala tkllifhm ma la ytyqwn min alaemal, qad atynak bdlalt mejzt min rabik tadulu ealaa sadaqana fi dewtna, walslamt min eadhab allah taealaa liman atabae hdah. 'iina rabak qad awha 'iilayna an eadhabah ealaa man kdhdhab wa'aerid ean dewth wshryeth"
  20,49,"qal fireawn lhma: fman rabukuma ya mwsa?"
  20,50,"qal lah mwsa: rabana aldhy 'aetaa kula shay' khalqah allayq bih ealaa hasan sneh, thuma hudana kl mkhlwq 'iilaa alantfae bima khalaqah allah lh"
  20,51,"qal fireawn lmwsa: fama shan al'umam alsabq? wama khabar alqurun almadyt, faqad sabaquna 'iilaa al'inkar walkfr?"
  20,52,"qal musaa lfrewn: eilm tilk alqurun fima faealat min dhlk eind rabiy fi allwh almhfwz, wala eilm li bh, laa yadilu rabiy fi 'afealih wahkamh, wala yansaa shyyana mmma ealamah mnha"
  20,53,"hw aladhi jaeal lakum al'ard myssart llantfae bha, wajaeal lakum fiha trqana kthyrt, wa'anzal min alsama' mtrana, fa'akhraj bih anwaeana mukhtalifat min alnbat"
  20,54,"klu - 'ayuha alnaas - min tayibat ma 'anbatna lkm, wareawa hywanatkm wbhaymkm. 'iina fi kl ma dhukr laelamat ealaa qudrat allh, wadaewat lwhdanyth w'ifradh balebadt, ldhwy aleqwl alslymt"